value:
Compressed scores of four arias, with incomplete texts (one without text), one aria in score (A, fl?, b), and two fragments.
Holograph manuscript in ink.
Watermark: "LVG" below fleur de lis over Strasbourg bend; countermark: "IV" (Burrows C130)
Contents:
1] p. 25, lines 1-4. Impari del mio core : [aria, S, b, HWV 216] -- [2] p. 25, line 5-10. Quant'invidio tua fortuna : [aria, S, b, HWV 221] -- [3] p. 26, line 1-4. Per da pace al mio tormento : [aria, S, b, HWV 220] Largo -- [4] p. 26, lines 5-8. [Untexted aria, S, bc (starts in C-3 clef and changes to C-1)] Larg[a]m[en]t[e]. -- [5] p. 26, lines 9-10. [Fragment for 1-2 trebles (on one stave) and bass in F major, 17 bars] -- [6] p. 27-28. Dell onda instabile : [aria, A, fl?, bc, HWV 214] -- [7] [Fragment for treble and bass in C major, 14? bars]
